document_data.caption: A glimpse of the historical Gate of the Fallen.
document_data.name: Gate of the Fallen
document_data.mainbody:
The '''Gate of the Fallen''' was a large monument located in the [[City of Brass]] in [[1367 DR]].{{AQ-time}}

The Gate of the Fallen was found within the ward of [[Castings]].
document_data.Description: Despite its name, the Gate of the Fallen was not a gate or a memorial to the [[efreeti]] dead. It was in fact a large decorated archway depicting scenes of the efreet dominating all other races found on the [[Elemental Plane of Fire]].
